name: Astrograces
description:
We receive this message from far, far away. The signal is really low, but you can hear the voices of the three explorers congratulation each other after the landing.

"Girls, we did it" was the only clear part of the message.

Illustration based on the painting of "The Three Graces" 1630 - 1635. Oil on oak panel. By Peter Paul Rubens

"Calm Synthesizer, B.wav" by InspectorJ (www.jshaw.co.uk) of Freesound.org
